{"tid":1336319,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【721】 重 溫 狗 隻 圍 堵 戰 術","createTime":"2019-07-21T02:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T03:27:15.000Z","uid":52609,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ca887a121ee7b2540660f60135181b789c43d92e","tid":1336319,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190719/large/1563531049_fc09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190719%2Flarge%2F1563531049_fc09.jpg&h=8ff797a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n立法會之戰。7.1接近午夜，警方先後由(1)龍匯道及(2)龍和道推進，先後施放多枚催淚彈，(3)逼使示威者沿添美道走到夏慤道，(4)再有另一隊警員在夏慤道由東向西驅趕去金鐘站及中環一帶。撇除是否有使用催淚彈的必要，這次行動的逃走路線相當清晰，亦沒有發生圍困情況。《蘋果》製圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190719/large/1563531057_cfa9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190719%2Flarge%2F1563531057_cfa9.jpg&h=1a494851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角之戰。在7日夜晚，當遊行人士轉到旺角彌敦道時，大批警員在亞皆老街設防，至晚上10時半開始行動，(1)先將示威者推向油麻地方向，(2)同時部署在朗豪坊的警員經奶路臣街及山東街推進，逼示威者向西洋菜南街走。(3)與此同時，另外兩隊警員再由波鞋街同豉油街夾擊，將大部份示威者趕去洗衣街花園及麥花臣方向，部份人就經小巷四散。當日警方行動明顯有升級，包圍較7.1嚴密，但仍然未如同沙田般封死所有去路。《蘋果》製圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190719/large/1563531065_0330.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190719%2Flarge%2F1563531065_0330.jpg&h=fbfe5c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田之戰。14日晚防暴警察於晚上約9時，(1)先三面夾擊聚集在源禾路十字路口的示威者，(2)同時封鎖担杆莆街路口，阻止人潮湧向沙田大會堂，逼示威者轉入橫壆街，(3)經其他商場再接駁天橋向新城市方向繼續離開，(4)但當大部份人進入新城市廣場後，始發現原來當時唯一離開的交通工具、通往沙田港鐵站的閘口已被警員封鎖，(5)另外有警員從大會堂百步梯推進，連同正在消費的一般市民，所有人被圍困在新城市範圍。(6)完成包圍後不久，大批全副武裝防暴警察即進入商場，形成「困獸鬥」局面，最終醸成流血衝突。《蘋果》製圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190719/large/1563531038_8f22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190719%2Flarge%2F1563531038_8f22.jpg&h=88d1ed57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「沸水戰術」英文為Kettling，字根來自水壺（Kettle），即警察有計劃地收縮封鎖線，如同熱水壺的外殼，盛載住比喻成熱燙沸水的示威者，以達致防止示威範圍擴散的目的。一般沸水戰術都會留有一個缺口，避免過度刺激及讓示威者有路可退，就如同蒸氣需要有出口去疏導；除非示威者不願離開並不斷從缺口湧入，否則不會將唯一出口合攏。《蘋果》製圖<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190720/59838152?fbclid=IwAR17alYFmIgNRbmx6VIjzR680pDiiX3UuWWHZt4EkcnOsaKmTWFSDzYE_7M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190720%2F59838152%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR17alYFmIgNRbmx6VIjzR680pDiiX3UuWWHZt4EkcnOsaKmTWFSDzYE_7M&d=3A6Iqvk0VBPdaidkhJ82W60J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=21723026\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190720%2F59838152%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR17alYFmIgNRbmx6VIjzR680pDiiX3UuWWHZt4EkcnOsaKmTWFSDzYE_7M&h=7a276c3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190720/59838152?fbclid=IwAR17alYFmIgNRbmx6VIjzR680pDiiX3UuWWHZt4EkcnOsaKmTWFSDzYE_7M</a>"},{"pid":"3e5328fd8f4586982962f9ea2efa9354701124a4","tid":1336319,"uid":48427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3abae786bb948167cbe975ee823af9d2e35778","tid":1336319,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:09:44.000Z","msg":"７２１見！<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力！<br />\n不分化不篤灰不割蓆不譴責！<br />\n<br />\n【721整合】整合Post！全部推哂上熱門！ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329038</a>"},{"pid":"9a35a593d3e7bb1b11bf4cfade606f7b98ac14c4","tid":1336319,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:12:51.000Z","msg":"７２１見！<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力！<br />\n不分化不篤灰不割蓆不譴責！<br />\n<br />\n【721整合】整合Post！全部推哂上熱門！ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329038\" data-aut